---
layout: "base"
title: "Kommunikations-Trainer | PUK Zürich"
description: "Kommunikations-Trainer: 8 Situationen aus Manie, Depression, Frühwarnung und Post-Episode. Welche Antwort hilft — und warum? PUK Zürich."
permalink: "/tools/komm-trainer/"
toolBackHref: "/modul/6/"
toolBackLabel: "Zurück zu Modul 6"
useSharedCSS: true
useNavJS: false
useToolCSS: true
---
{% block headCSS %}
<style>
body{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;color:#1c2b3a;background:#FAFAF7;min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
.tool-nav{width:100%;background:rgba(254,252,248,0.92);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(16px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-warm);padding:14px 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50}
.wrap{width:100%;max-width:600px;padding:32px 20px 48px;flex:1}
.hdr{text-align:center;margin-bottom:24px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.94),rgba(247,250,251,0.88));border:1px solid var(--border-warm-md);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:26px 24px 24px;box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(28,43,58,0.08);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hdr h1{font-family:'DM Serif Display',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(1.3rem,3.5vw,1.7rem);font-weight:700;color:#2a211b;margin:0 0 8px;letter-spacing:-0.02em}
.prog{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-bottom:24px}.prog div{flex:1;height:4px;border-radius:2px;background:#e6f4f2;transition:background 0.4s}.prog .done{background:#1E656D}.prog .cur{background:#a7d9d5}
.card{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#fff 0%,#fbfcfd 100%);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);border:1px solid var(--border-warm);box-shadow:0 12px 34px rgba(28,43,58,0.08);overflow:hidden;transition:opacity 0.3s}
.card.fade{opacity:0}
.card-body{padding:24px 28px}
.phase-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px}
.phase-badge{padding:4px 12px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em}
.phase-m{background:#fef3e2;color:#B45309}.phase-d{background:#eef3f8;color:#5b7fa5}.phase-f{background:#e6f4f2;color:#1E656D}.phase-n{background:#f0f0f0;color:#475569}
.phase-count{font-size:0.75rem;color:#475569}
.sit{font-family:'DM Serif Display',Georgia,serif;font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;color:#1c2b3a;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:20px}
.olbl{font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:700;color:#475569;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:12px}
.opt-btn{width:100%;padding:14px 18px;border-radius:var(--radius-md);border:1px solid var(--border-warm-md);background:#fff;color:#475569;font-size:0.85rem;text-align:left;cursor:pointer;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;line-height:1.5;transition:background-color 0.25s ease,color 0.25s ease,border-color 0.25s ease;margin-bottom:10px;-webkit-appearance:none}
.opt-btn:disabled{cursor:default}
.opt-btn.correct{border:2px solid #0d7a5f;background:#e6f4f2;color:#1c2b3a;font-weight:600}
.opt-btn.wrong{border:2px solid #9A3412;background:#FEF2F2;color:#9A3412}
.opt-btn.dimmed{border-color:var(--border-warm);color:#8DD4D9}
.fb{padding:12px 16px;margin-top:-4px;margin-bottom:10px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:0.8rem;line-height:1.6}
.fb-ok{background:#FAFAF7;border-left:3px solid #0d7a5f;color:#1c2b3a}
.fb-no{background:#FEF2F2;border-left:3px solid #9A3412;color:#9A3412}
.mark{font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:800;margin-right:6px}
.btn-next{width:100%;padding:12px;border-radius:var(--radius-md);border:none;background:#1E656D;color:#fff;font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;margin-top:8px}
.res{padding:36px 32px;text-align:center}
.res-circle{width:80px;height:80px;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);margin:0 auto 20px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border:3px solid}
.res-circle span{font-family:'DM Serif Display',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.7rem;font-weight:700}
.res h2{font-family:'DM Serif Display',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:#1c2b3a;margin:0 0 12px}
.res p{font-size:0.85rem;color:#475569;line-height:1.65;margin:0 0 24px}
.rules{background:#FAFAF7;border-radius:var(--radius-md);padding:16px 20px;text-align:left;margin-bottom:20px}
.rules-title{font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:700;color:#1E656D;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;margin-bottom:10px}
.rules p{font-size:0.85rem;color:#1c2b3a;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 8px}.rules p:last-child{margin:0}
.btns{display:flex;gap:10px}.btns button{flex:1;padding:12px;border-radius:var(--radius-md);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer}
.btn-r{border:1px solid var(--border-warm-md);background:#fff;color:#475569}
.btn-c{border:none;background:#1E656D;color:#fff}
@media(max-width:480px){
  .wrap{padding:20px 14px 36px}
  .card-body{padding:16px}
  .opt-btn{padding:12px 14px}
}
</style>
{% endblock %}
{% block nav %}
{% include "nav-tool.njk" %}
{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
<main class="wrap" id="main-content">
  <div class="hdr">
<div class="tool-breadcrumb"><a href="/">Startseite</a><span class="sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span><a href="{{ toolBackHref }}">{{ toolBackLabel | replace("Zurück zu ", "") }}</a><span class="sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span>Kommunikations-Trainer</span></div>
<div class="tool-glyph" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M9 12H25C28.3 12 31 14.7 31 18V19C31 22.3 28.3 25 25 25H18L13 30V25H9C5.7 25 3 22.3 3 19V18C3 14.7 5.7 12 9 12Z" fill="#A8E4E8"/><path d="M21 8H31C34.3 8 37 10.7 37 14V15C37 18.3 34.3 21 31 21H29V25L24 21H21C17.7 21 15 18.3 15 15V14C15 10.7 17.7 8 21 8Z" fill="#1E656D"/></svg></div><div class="badge">Modul 6 — Übung</div><h1>Kommunikations-Trainer</h1><p>Acht Situationen aus Manie, Depression, Frühwarnung und der Zeit nach einer Krise. Nicht die perfekte Antwort zählt, sondern ein klareres Gefühl dafür, was in welcher Lage eher hilft.</p></div>
  <div class="prog" id="prog"></div>
  <div class="card" id="card" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true"></div>
